Text.val: -- SREG_ID must exists in table SREG and in table HURG where allowed regions are defined per user

SQL_STMT_U.val: select A.SFEX_ADMNO, A.SFEX_CLNTNO, (select count(*) from :1/SFER where SFER_ERRORCODE > 0 and SFER_SFEX_NO in (select SFEX_NO from :1/SFEX B where B.SFEX_SCFH_NO = :2 and B.SFEX_ADMNO = A.SFEX_ADMNO and B.SFEX_CLNTNO = A.SFEX_CLNTNO)) from :1/SFEX A where SFEX_SCFH_NO = :2 group by A.SFEX_ADMNO, A.SFEX_CLNTNO order by A.SFEX_ADMNO, A.SFEX_CLNTNO for fetch only
